body:
The share command aborts if the cell type is a reduce operation. This fix prevents the abort by supporting `$reduce_and/or/xor/xnor/bool`.

Added the following test that would fail before the fix:

```
read_verilog <<EOF
module top(a, b, s, y);
	input wire [7:0] a;
	input wire [7:0] b;
	input wire s;
	output wire y;
	assign y = s ? |a : |b;
endmodule
EOF

share -force
```

